<inglise> Statements regarding Regulation (EC, ECSC, Euratom) No 762/2001 of 9 April 2001 amending the Financial Regulation of 21 December 1977 applicable to the general budget of the European Communities as regards separating the internal audit function from the ex ante financial control function </inglise>
<eesti> Avaldused seoses n&otilde;ukogu 9. aprilli 2001. aasta m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;, EST&Uuml;, Euratom) nr 762/2001, millega muudetakse Euroopa &uuml;henduste &uuml;ldeelarve suhtes kohaldatavat 21. detsembri 1977. aasta finantsm&auml;&auml;rust seoses siseauditi eraldamisega eelnevast finantskontrollist </eesti>
<inglise> 1. "The European Parliament and the Council reached a broad convergence of views on separating the internal audit function from the ex ante financial control function. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. "Euroopa Parlament ja n&otilde;ukogu on j&otilde;udnud enam-v&auml;hem &uuml;ksmeelele siseauditi eraldamise suhtes eelnevast finantskontrollist. </eesti>
<inglise> In conformity with new Article 24a(3) of the Financial Regulation, they confirm their willingness to implement internally the separation of the internal audit function from the ex ante financial control function. </inglise>
<eesti> Finantsm&auml;&auml;ruse uue artikli 24a l&otilde;ike 3 kohaselt kinnitavad nad oma valmisolekut eraldada oma siseaudit oma eelnevast sisekontrollist. </eesti>
<inglise> They will carry out this separation as soon as their internal control systems and procedures are fully operational." </inglise>
<eesti> Nad teevad selle eraldamise niipea, kui nende sisekontrollis&uuml;steemid ja -menetlused toimivad t&auml;ies ulatuses." </eesti>
<inglise> 2. "The Commission considers that the internal audit should be carried out in accordance with the relevant international rules, as laid down by the proposal amending the Commission Regulation of 1993 laying down detailed rules for the implementation of the Financial Regulation, adopted on 15 November 2000 and currently under consultation at the European Parliament and the Council, and on the basis of a risk assessment, as provided for in the proposed revision of the Financial Regulation of 21 December 1977 adopted by the Commission on 26 July 2000." </inglise>
<eesti> 2. "Komisjon leiab, et siseaudit peaks toimuma koosk&otilde;las asjakohaste rahvusvaheliste eeskirjadega, nagu on s&auml;testatud 15. novembril 2000 vastuv&otilde;etud ettepanekus finantsm&auml;&auml;ruse &uuml;ksikasjalike rakenduseeskirjade kehtestamist k&auml;sitleva komisjoni 1993. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse muutmise kohta, mida Euroopa Parlament ja n&otilde;ukogu hetkel arutavad, ja p&otilde;hinema riskihindamisel, nagu on s&auml;testatud 21. detsembri 1977. aasta finantsm&auml;&auml;ruse muutmisettepanekus, mille komisjon v&otilde;ttis vastu 26. juulil 2000." </eesti>
 